      </div>
      <div class="services-row">
        <img class="img-cattle" src="/images/cattle-3.jpg">
        <h3 class="service-heading-cattle">Cattle</h3>
        <p class="service-desc-cattle">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor
